Organization.name: Urban Pathways
Organization.description: Urban Pathways supports and guides unhoused men and women by providing shelter and services that improve their quality of life.

Services.name: Shower
Services.description: You get a bar of soap and a towel for 15 minutes. Lockers are available to those who complete an intake.

Services.name: Clothing Pantry
Services.description: Clothing is for clients and does not require a referral letter. Clothing is very limited.
